<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
{% include 'head.html' %}
<body>
    <div id="container">
        <a class="header" href="."><h1>IndieCert</h1></a>

        <p class="warn">
            This is an <strong>EXPERIMENTAL</strong> service. No warranty!
        </p>

        <p>
            IndieCert is a service to authenticate to services around the web using your
            home page URL as an identity without requiring a password by using secure
            client certificates! Check out the <a href="faq">FAQ</a> for more details!
            <a href="faq#supportedServices">Here</a> is a list of supported services.
        </p>

        <h2>Try It!</h2>
        <p>Provide your home page URL you want to use as your identity:</p>

        <form class="authenticate" method="post" action="_indieauth/auth">
            <label for="me">https://</label><input id="me" required type="text" name="me" placeholder="example.org">
            <input type="hidden" name="redirect_to" value="/account">
            <input class="info" type="submit" value="Sign In">
        </form>
        {% include 'footer.html' %}
    </div> <!-- /container -->
</body>
</html>
